
PALADIN : : : : : : : : : : : : -ALLIANCE- : : : : : : : : : : : : : : BARD


      Welcome to the Bard-Paladin Alliance.  You now wear the colors of
      the two orders; The red, white and silver of the Paladins and the
      black, midnight blue and silver of the Bards.  The Alliance has
      been formed to help facilitate the destruction of the forces of
      evil throughout the realms of magic known collectively as Nirvana.
      Power to the Alliance!  Type <a_powers> to see Alliance abilities.


